wiki.content: The Between The Cheats Songfacts says: This Amy Winehouse composition was recorded in London in May 2008 for potential inclusion on her third album. Tragically the English songstress passed away before the LP was completed, but it was included on her postosthumous long player, Lioness: Hidden Treasures. According to frequent Winehouse cohort Salaam Remi, who produced the song, the track’s heavy doo wop influence, "shows one of the main directions in which she was heading."
